{"tid":1637569,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰●黃大仙】保一學子撕毀「禁罩」通告 高呼蒙面無罪　 　","createTime":"2019-10-08T04:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T09:38:27.000Z","uid":308020,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c35832d69d88ddd2016dc94f42391d3495572e","tid":1637569,"uid":308020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"今日是《禁止蒙面規例》實施後的第一個上課天，雖然教育局上周五發通告指學生在校內外均不應戴口罩，但學界無懼打壓和白色恐怖，多區學校今早都有大批同學戴口罩回校。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【你問我答4pm Live】禁蒙面惡法出爐 快必&times;前線學生記者齊鬧爆克警記招<br />\n<br />\n在黃大仙，區內Band1中學、保良區第一張永慶中學中五生Percy周五收到學校通告，表示感到十分憤怒，班上全部同學均不贊成政府強推蒙面法，部份人更即場撕毀通告，將紙碎撒在操場上，並高呼蒙面無罪，立法無理。<br />\n<br />\n對於教育局以不應將政治帶入校園為由禁蒙面，Percy認為是不可接受，因為政治是通識科的必修課題。他今日一出門便戴上口罩，目的是告訴市民及其他同學，繼續表達意見無需恐懼，面對極權政府，人民毋須懼怕。Percy指4個月來的抗爭，令學校風氣有所轉變，雖然低年級學生年紀尚輕，對政治未有太多取態，但不少高年級同學變得積極議政。他直言抗爭的確令忙碌的學生生活百上加斤，對時間分配是一大考驗，但他亦不會放棄，比起對學業上的些微影響，香港的未來更為重要。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【毅進制的錯】的士疑蓄意撞斷少女腳 警漏夜發稿僅稱司機被私了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rq4Fjjv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRq4Fjjv.jpg&h=b8dcc7aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有黃大仙區Band1中學學生戴面具上學。黃麗英、文兆麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QYuW60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QYuW60.jpg&h=7f3fbc16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎同學會一直戴到林鄭撤回惡法為止。黃麗英、文兆麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/saXzoM6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsaXzoM6.jpg&h=7abce64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃大仙區學生在校門外派發口罩。黃麗英、文兆麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HcQdEky.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHcQdEky.jpg&h=c60e4170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPercy表示面對極權政府，人民毋須懼怕。。黃麗英、文兆麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPoreTZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPoreTZ.jpg&h=e95bab90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生上周五當場撕毀通告。黃麗英、文兆麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fkPxUT5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfkPxUT5.jpg&h=0daffc6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生上周五當場撕毀通告。黃麗英、文兆麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191008/60128831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60128831&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIpFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=4b33ceab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60128831&h=6160c193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191008/60128831</a>"},{"pid":"a18aa6ab6b7c4997442973e3016885f37ae9201c","tid":1637569,"uid":258208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:47:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f05537fd71ef4904feae8b78695bb78c1c125e1","tid":1637569,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:22:50.000Z","msg":"幾時搞番個全民撕紙日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dafd619f59a22779850686bbaedadd8a1b410a1","tid":1637569,"uid":12414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"咁樣先似band 1學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}